---
// Rendered by /marketplace/[id].astro when a non-owner hits the URL of a
// listing past the 21-day freshness clock. HTTP 200 keeps the URL stable +
// indexable-but-empty rather than 404-broken. The owner can bring the
// listing back into public view by bumping (which resets the clock); the
// next request then renders the full detail page at the same URL.
//
// v1 DE only — the kiosk i18n store lives in client-side localStorage and
// isn't reachable from an .astro file (SSR). Flip to a client-rendered
// Svelte island if multi-locale matters later.
---

<div class="market-unavailable">
  <div class="market-unavailable__panel">
    <p class="market-unavailable__kicker">Markt · Schillerkiez</p>
    <h1 class="market-unavailable__title">Diese Anzeige ist nicht mehr verfügbar.</h1>
    <p class="market-unavailable__subtitle">
      Möglicherweise wurde sie zurückgezogen oder nicht aktualisiert.
    </p>
    <a href="/marketplace" class="market-unavailable__cta">← Zurück zum Markt</a>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .market-unavailable {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 16px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .market-unavailable__panel {
    background: var(--k-paper-warm, #efe9d7);
    border: 1.5px dashed var(--k-rule, #c9c0a8);
    border-radius: var(--k-radius-md, 6px);
    padding: 36px 28px;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 480px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .market-unavailable__kicker {
    font-family: var(--k-font-mono, monospace);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--k-wine, #b23a5b);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .market-unavailable__title {
    font-family: var(--k-font-display, sans-serif);
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    color: var(--k-ink, #1b1a17);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 0 0 12px;
  }

  .market-unavailable__subtitle {
    font-family: var(--k-font-serif, Georgia, serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--k-ink-soft, #5a5650);
    margin: 0 0 22px;
  }

  .market-unavailable__cta {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--k-font-mono, monospace);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--k-ink, #1b1a17);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-style: dashed;
    text-decoration-color: var(--k-rule, #c9c0a8);
    text-underline-offset: 4px;
    padding: 4px 8px;
    transition: color 150ms ease;
  }

  .market-unavailable__cta:hover {
    color: var(--k-wine, #b23a5b);
  }
</style>
